Core Legend
	‚Ä¢	F ‚Äì state vector
	‚Ä¢	\dot F ‚Äì rate of change of state
	‚Ä¢	\mathcal{R}(F) ‚Äì relational flow
	‚Ä¢	M, N ‚Äì metrics (state, gauge)
	‚Ä¢	A ‚Äì gauge/context field
